## 1 Definitions

Direct value capture‚Äîmany-to-one, closed, permissioned.

Diffuse value capture‚Äîmany-to-many, open, permissionless.

Direct and diffuse value capture exist on a spectrum, extremes on both ends are almost always unworkable.

